title: TikFinity | TikTok LIVE API
text: TikFinity offers you a WebSocket endpoint that allows you to receive all events of your TikTok livestream. You can use it to build your own games and interactive widgets! The TikFinity Desktop App must run on the same computer! Login Start Page Hey, you don't have any new notifications! Discover tips, insights, and the latest updates to help you get the most out of our tools.
